    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深渊地牢 是一款快节奏、双摇杆射击 Roguelike 游戏。在有限的资源下，选择不同的道具，创造强大的组合，挑战更高的难度，解锁新的技能和武器。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157890/extras/d37e6e704c86c515e42695701c16223b.webp?t=1764335049\" width=627 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在狭小空间内快速反应战斗。后坐力与射程的平衡，风险与奖励的选择。移动抵消后坐力，冲刺移动之间更高的操作空间。多样的怪物攻击形式和房间陷阱创造了独特的战斗体验</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157890/extras/442c49ea7bef95ee12992a31f86795d2.poster.avif?t=1764335049\" width=626 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157890/extras/442c49ea7bef95ee12992a31f86795d2.webm?t=1764335049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157890/extras/442c49ea7bef95ee12992a31f86795d2.mp4?t=1764335049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157890/extras/a9ac2a2e08656f871f6e23a66a282dd5.webp?t=1764335049\" width=627 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个关卡提供的资源都是有限的，你需要根据现有的武器、技能、道具做出最优的选择。难度会不断增加，直到到达boss房间。每一个房间的选择都会在以后产生不同的后果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157890/extras/b3849891a4c69ea6f6004d1b7afba433.avif?t=1764335049\" width=626 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157890/extras/209c43b6d5f5a1462839ae6c2d460999.poster.avif?t=1764335049\" width=626 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157890/extras/209c43b6d5f5a1462839ae6c2d460999.webm?t=1764335049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157890/extras/209c43b6d5f5a1462839ae6c2d460999.mp4?t=1764335049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157890/extras/e220b3f27e0e815f0f9a3a7ee1312ea8.webp?t=1764335049\" width=627 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武器、技能、道具都可以通过有限的升级来获得更大的收益。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157890/extras/ced8fee77abe4cc2f8e3998c7abde550.poster.avif?t=1764335049\" width=626 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157890/extras/ced8fee77abe4cc2f8e3998c7abde550.webm?t=1764335049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157890/extras/ced8fee77abe4cc2f8e3998c7abde550.mp4?t=1764335049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武器、技能、道具都可以进行有限次数的升级，以获得更大的收益。不同的技能，搭配不同的武器，需要不同的强化方向，但有限的装备槽位让道具的选择变得更加重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157890/extras/5801074c742246435d2294bbfa90f96c.poster.avif?t=1764335049\" width=626 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157890/extras/5801074c742246435d2294bbfa90f96c.webm?t=1764335049\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157890/extras/5801074c742246435d2294bbfa90f96c.mp4?t=1764335049\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
